  "3024130": {
    "name": "泡泡镇餐厅物语",
    "steam_appid": 3024130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《泡泡镇餐厅物语》是一款适合 1 至 4 人玩的有趣合作模拟与沙盒游戏。在这里，猫咪、狐狸、浣熊和其他毛茸茸的小伙伴们在举办真正的美食盛宴。经营你的餐厅：钓取新鲜食材，赶在饥肠辘辘的顾客离开前迅速完成订单——一秒钟也不要浪费！单独作战或召集好友，一起征服迷你游戏，探索繁华夜城，并将你的生意推向一个连街边小狗都会羡慕的高度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/8a4a23263cf402b86da89e26b5d24315.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/8a4a23263cf402b86da89e26b5d24315.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/8a4a23263cf402b86da89e26b5d24315.mp4?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/4bc158c99cc3e2cfeaf5994557435723.avif?t=1769170344\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断取得成就，扩展并升级你的餐厅。从简陋的厨房开始，逐步增加烤箱、炸锅和更多设备。白天订单不断，而夜晚则是放松并为新一天做准备的好时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/2bc4ecb65c0bcf176170e81dd2721a1f.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/2bc4ecb65c0bcf176170e81dd2721a1f.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/2bc4ecb65c0bcf176170e81dd2721a1f.mp4?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/39ff9bca0a1ee66a565e1231960fac9d.avif?t=1769170344\" width=700 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进一个充满机遇的半开放城市——抢到超赞的奖励，顺便参与各种任务；穿梭在街头，遇见奇趣 NPC，从他们手中获得令人兴奋的任务和超值优惠；还有趣味迷你游戏助你提升生意……不断探索，准备迎接层出不穷的惊喜与挑战！ 在《泡泡镇的餐厅物语》中，你的造型完全由你决定。选择你的图腾动物——从牛到狼，还有熊猫——搭配出能展现你创意与商业头脑的皮肤。不论是严肃的厨师帽还是搞笑的爪印头巾，混搭细节，打造出独一无二的风格，完美衬托你的美食传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/6501f9602cfb293bc0fd90b2654bf803.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/6501f9602cfb293bc0fd90b2654bf803.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/6501f9602cfb293bc0fd90b2654bf803.mp4?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/93370e600df21bfc200e358049245afb.avif?t=1769170344\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >早晨是钓鱼、逛街和约会好友的时间，而夜晚则突然安静下来。你可以悠闲地探索餐厅，或者早早上床以加速迎来新一天。每天你都会收到餐厅账单：评分越高，奖励越丰厚！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/64663e7eac8acfe2093edd846f646261.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/64663e7eac8acfe2093edd846f646261.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/64663e7eac8acfe2093edd846f646261.mp4?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/087f9600a051d8425c69de6d6dc53843.avif?t=1769170344\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  每个任务都有一个迷你游戏——抓住时机，按下正确的按钮，并密切关注指示器。无论是烹饪还是钓鱼，每个动作都需要你积极参与。随着进度的推进，挑战性也会逐步增加，所以绝不会无聊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/78dd60eebb4792c58355a4c31e4b9722.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/78dd60eebb4792c58355a4c31e4b9722.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/78dd60eebb4792c58355a4c31e4b9722.mp4?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/4e649aee4ad4513d9c07c161ba912d16.avif?t=1769170344\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想象一下：你收到市政厅发来的 VIP 邀请邮件，必须立刻升级餐厅以留下深刻印象；或者参加一场美食大赛，在限定时间内加入必备食材——最佳厨师将获得一张提高声誉并吸引新顾客的权威证书。我们的任务旨在为你的游戏体验增添刺激与乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/e8c1918b8f8cd8b0e59c280a78ef99e9.poster.avif?t=1769170344\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024130/extras/e8c1918b8f8cd8b0e59c280a78ef99e9.webm?t=1769170344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厨房火热运转，已无回头路！如果你对自己的能力充满信心，就勇敢投入这场动物狂欢，证明你绝对是泡泡大师！ </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 韩语, 波兰语, 俄语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 日语, 瑞典语",
